  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">La luce rivela e illumina, ma è anche in grado di creare illusioni, come miraggi nel deserto che possono ingannare gli ingiusti e offrire al mago una diversione inaspettata.<br/></span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>SCIPLEMENTARI</strong><br/></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Quando si sceglie questo segreto, si impara il @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.oIzA2MEHwxhtQneU]{Minor Illusion}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">e @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Bnn9Nzajixvow9xi]{Light}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">cantrip, e quando ottengono un livello nel segreto si imparano gli incantesimi corrispondenti indicati nella seguente tabella:<br/></span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>Cantrips:</strong>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.oIzA2MEHwxhtQneU]{Minor Illusion}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Bnn9Nzajixvow9xi]{Light}<br/></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>1° livello:</strong>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.LWTUqKkUQdMAmOe0]{Color Spray}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.BrBZdCCrJRIVg7YX]{Silent Image}<br/></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>2° livello:</strong>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.JbxsYXxSOTZbf9I0]{Spiritual Weapon}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.bV3yun6MIuFj71Er]{Moonbeam}<br/></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>3° livello:</strong>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.BP3GCwa66IAw1yTG]{Daylight}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.6g3WLOZ2u0EbaLAd]{Hypnotic Pattern}<br/></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>4° livello:</strong>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.gXtzz9t1DTzJeLr4]{Locate Creature}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.sTIkQK7KuQNOyY0C]{Hallucinatory Terrain}<br/></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>5° livello:</strong>@Compendium[world.spells-historia.dsO5vt30j2QUAO]{Dawn}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.mbFw57uyfLkyiw5k]{Seeming}<br/></span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>MISTERI</strong></span><br/><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.profession-featuression.yJ4yJAlZGXyXtF0H]{Founding Mystery: Without Fear}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.profession-featuression.ZWgsOHVV0OSI15ry]{Major Mystery: Glare}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.profession-featuression.1weIpdXBf1XzpdcR]{Greater Mystery: Full of Light}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.profession-featuression.VGarVRYVUEPOJD3N]{Universal Mystery: Blazing Halo}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>METAMAGICO DEL SECRET</strong><br/></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Quando raggiungi il terzo livello in questo Segreto, sei riuscito a modificare gli incantesimi che possono lanciare, adattandoli alle tue esigenze attuali e impara le seguenti opzioni metamagiche.</span> <br style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\"/></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.profession-featuression-features.v7HWKi3xHaSwodoZ]{Metamagic: Incanto maggiore}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.profession-featuression.xFBGHjhAlAQBl09J]{Metamagic: Quickened Spell}</span></p>",
